    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小贴士：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1.F11：切换全屏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2.若显示器分辨率过低，导致屏幕下方出现截断，可在【设置】中调整游戏分辨率。调整后重启游戏即可生效。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>（若看不到【设置】，请在游戏标题画面处，当光标位于[新游戏]时，按2下[方向键下]，再按[回车键]即可。）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3.使用[方向键左/右]，切换设置内容。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162790/extras/2d23578478f26b644f33a4beb9f0462f.webp?t=1770345019\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某日，王国艾涅露弗的北方堡垒遭到了来自兽人的侵略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为王国的公主，普莉西亚掌握着只有王族才能使用的【陷阱魔法】，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了王国，普莉西亚决心活用魔法抵御兽人的进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162790/extras/930eb57c84213306e6d1f045f093d9b7.webp?t=1770345019\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D和2D融合的游戏机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塔防</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第三人称射击</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美的3D模型</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162790/extras/f9b084fef737ed9147e0e53ac18d176b.webp?t=1770345019\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >□地图画面</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色移动：WASD/鼠标左键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >确定：Z键/鼠标左键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >取消/菜单：X键/鼠标右键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >菜单画面表示：X键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升移动速度：Shift键</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >□塔防战斗时</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色移动：WASD</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视角面向前方：F键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >射击/点击按钮：鼠标左键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动视角：拖拽鼠标右键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩大・缩小视角：鼠标滚轮</p></li></ul>",
